a.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1954%2c20220831%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,簡,1954,20220831,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1954","JDATE":"20220831","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}